## Notes

- **Total** counts all submitted Cabrillo logs for that contest and year
- **High/Low/QRP** from `CATEGORY-POWER:` header (not all logs include this)
- **Multi-Op** includes MULTI-ONE, MULTI-TWO, MULTI-UNLIMITED, and MULTI-DISTRIBUTED
- Some years may be missing if contest logs are not yet available for download
- Checklog and SWL entries are included in totals

